data.description: Located in the heart of Austell, this 0.44-acre parcel offers a unique opportunity for both investors and home builders. Situated on a dead-end street, this large lot is perfect for someone looking to build in a non-HOA community. Nestled within Cobb County, this land lot boasts a prime location with easy access to local amenities, schools, and parks. 2023-11-27
